=== 热带气旋警告 ===
热带风暴鲍勃于8月16日获名数小时后，[[巴哈马政治|巴哈马政府]]向[[安德罗斯岛|安德罗斯岛]]至[[伊柳塞拉岛|伊柳塞拉岛]]之间的西北群岛发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]。气旋转向北上后，预计群岛不会受到热带风暴强度大风影响，上述警告因此中止。8月17日鲍勃升级成飓风前不久，美国国家飓风中心向[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]][[霍里县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|霍里县]]里特河向北直至[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]][[弗吉尼亚海滩|弗吉尼亚海滩]]之间的[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]沿海地区发布飓风观察预警。约四小时后，上述预警又升级成飓风警告。8月17日，弗吉尼亚海滩向北至[[特拉华州|特拉华州]][[亨洛彭角|亨洛彭角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Henlopen}}）收到飓风观察预警。8月18日，鲍勃沿[[中大西洋地区|中大西洋地区]]各州海岸线平行移动，上述飓风观察预警又升级成飓风警告。当天下午，包括[[诺福克_(弗吉尼亚州)|诺福克]]在内的[[切萨皮克湾|下切萨皮克湾]]地区接获热带风暴警告。<ref name="TCR17">{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | title = Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report Page Seventeen | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim17.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210358/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim17.gif}}</ref>

8月18日晚，由于气象机构预测风暴会直接袭击新英格兰南部，因而又有大范围地区接获飓风警告。警告范围从特拉华州亨洛彭角一直延伸到马萨诸塞州的[[普利茅斯_(麻萨诸塞州)|普利茅斯]]，并且包括[[长岛_(纽约州)|长岛]]和[[长岛海湾|长岛海湾]]。8月19日清晨，北卡罗莱纳州了望岬（{{lang|en|Cape Lookout}}）以南地区的热带气旋警告停止生效，飓风警告范围向北延伸到包括缅因州[[东港_(缅因州)|东港]]以南地区。[[加拿大飓风中心|加拿大飓风中心]]从当晚开始向[[加拿大大西洋省份|加拿大大西洋省份]]发布警告。[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]、[[爱德华王子岛|爱德华王子岛]]和新不伦瑞克都收到大风和暴雨警告。<ref name="TCR17" />截至8月20日早上，美国境内的所有热带气旋警告都已停止生效，但就在鲍勃的残留进入加拿大东部前，[[罗克兰_(缅因州)|罗克兰]]至东港间的缅因州沿海地区曾短暂进入热带风暴警告生效状态。气旋离开加拿大大西洋省份后，当地的风暴警告停止生效。<ref name="TCR18">{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | title = Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report Page Eighteen | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim18.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213208/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim18.gif | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-03}}</ref>

=== 中大西洋地区和南、北卡罗莱纳州 ===
8月17日收到飓风警告后<ref name="TCR17" />，北卡罗莱纳州最远离大陆的多个岛屿发布强制撤离令。地方车流量大增，警方为此提供协助，估计有五至十万人离开。人员疏散期间，部分路段因堵塞等原因造成的延误超过三小时。虽有大量人员撤离，但估计还是有五万人选择留在家中静待风暴过去。考虑到飓风强度的狂风可能对桥上行人和车辆安全构成重大威胁，当地有多座桥梁在气旋来袭前封闭。[[美国国家公园管理局|美国国家公园管理局]]驻北卡罗莱纳州办事处将[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]各地的露营地关闭，以防万一。<ref name="GBT1">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = Gettysburg Times | date = 1991-08-19 | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | title = Hurricane Bob Lashes North Carolina | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TboxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AucFAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20bob%20north%20carolina%20evacuation&pg=7030%2C1973320 | archive-date = 2017-04-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170404164142/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TboxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AucFAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20bob%20north%20carolina%20evacuation&pg=7030%2C1973320 | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[加特利县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|加特利县]]还开设有一间避难所<ref name="KD1">{{cite news | author = Anita Snow | agency = Associated Press) | newspaper = Kingman Daily Miner | date = 1991-08-20 | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | title = New England bracing for strike by Hurricane Bob | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HHsLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=iFMDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20bob%20north%20carolina%20evacuation&pg=5877%2C6250581 | archive-date = 2017-04-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170404160809/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HHsLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=iFMDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20bob%20north%20carolina%20evacuation&pg=5877%2C6250581 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。弗吉尼亚州的[[兰利空军基地|兰利空军基地]]有125架飞机转移到[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[代顿_(俄亥俄州)|代顿]]的[[赖特-帕特森空军基地|赖特-帕特森空军基地]]。[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]沿海地区有约400人疏散，[[大洋城_(马里兰州)|大洋城]]的风暴应急物资销量大幅上升。更北面的[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]有多家赌场准备沙袋保护楼房，还用胶带封住窗户。<ref name="KD1" />

纽约州[[苏福克县_(纽约州)|苏福克县]]应急官员未能及时决定是否要向沿海地区居民发布撤离令，导致政府职能被强加到公众头上。截至8月19日晚，该县仍未发布撤离令，但还是进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]并开设有多个救灾中心。<ref>{{cite news | author = Charles V. Zehren | publisher = Newsday | date = 1991-08-20 | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/doc/278413840.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=By%20Charles%20V.%20Zehren.%20STAFF%20WRITER.%20Pat%20Wiedenkeller&pub=Newsday%20(Combined%20editions)&edition=&startpage=&desc=HURRICANE%20BOB%20Officials%20Unclear%20on%20Evacuation | title = Hurricane Bob: Officials Unclear on Evacuation | archive-date = 2017-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171025155221/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/doc/278413840.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=By%20Charles%20V.%20Zehren.%20STAFF%20WRITER.%20Pat%20Wiedenkeller&pub=Newsday%20(Combined%20editions)&edition=&startpage=&desc=HURRICANE%20BOB%20Officials%20Unclear%20on%20Evacuation | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]在长岛开设四间避难所，风暴期间有约800人前来躲避<ref name="fema1">{{cite web | author = FEMA Headquarters | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | title = Situation Report — Hurricane Bob | year = 1991 | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084427/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/fema01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/fema01.gif | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。

=== 新英格兰和加拿大 ===
考虑到飓风可能造成的重大破坏，[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]和罗得岛州政府在鲍勃抵达新英格兰前宣布进入紧急状态。所有州政府工作人员接到提前回家、为应对风暴来袭做准备的通知。[[康涅狄格州议会|康涅狄格州议会]]取消州预算主题会议，州长[[小洛厄尔·魏克尔|小洛厄尔·魏克尔]]（{{lang|en|Lowell P. Weicker, Jr.}}）启动应急行动中心。[[格罗顿_(康涅狄格州)|格罗顿]]驻扎的潜艇离开港口，在水下静待风暴过去。面对气旋威胁，中大西洋地区和新英格兰各地的飞机和火车停运。<ref name="TDR1">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Daily Reporter | date = 1991-08-21 | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | title = Hurricane Bob lashes North Carolina; Long Island braces for a direct hit | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=a1orAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5dkEAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20bob%20north%20carolina%20evacuation&pg=1548%2C5939935 | archive-date = 2017-04-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170404173057/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=a1orAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5dkEAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20bob%20north%20carolina%20evacuation&pg=1548%2C5939935 | dead-url = no }}</ref>美国红十字会在康涅狄格州的16个社区共计开设23间避难所，还在邻近的罗得岛州开设有40间避难所<ref name="fema1" />。除红十字会开设的以外，两州还另有25个避难所<ref name="fema2">{{cite web | author = FEMA Headquarters | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | title = Situation Report — Hurricane Bob | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121026030652/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/fema02.gif | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/fema02.gif | format = GIF | year = 1991 | archivedate = 2012-10-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。罗得岛州共有约3500人疏散，其中单[[布洛克岛|布洛克岛]]（{{lang|en|Block Island}}）就有2000人。另外，还有多人在防灾准备期间受伤<ref name="ri">{{cite report | author = Valley/Sisson, Providence, Rhode Island National Weather Service | date = 1991-08-23 | title = Preliminary Survey on Hurricane Bob... First Issue | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshpvd05.gif | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070739/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshpvd05.gif}}</ref>。

马萨诸塞州[[鳕鱼角|鳕鱼角]]有数以千计的居民疏散，导致[[萨加莫尔大桥|萨加莫尔大桥]]（{{lang|en|Sagamore Bridge}}）严重堵塞，堵车路段长达18公里<ref name="wp820">{{cite news |author=Michael Specter |newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |date=1991-08-20 |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20130209042705/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/national/longterm/hurricane/archives/bob91.htm |archivedate=2013-02-09 |accessdate=2016-09-10 |title=Hurricane Rakes New England |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/national/longterm/hurricane/archives/bob91.htm |publisher=The Washington Post Company |deadurl=no }}</ref>。当地开设有九间避难所<ref name="fema2" />，之后挤满前来躲避的人员<ref name="wp820" />。全州共有约五万人离开家园，其中6500人躲入避难所<ref name="chant">{{cite report | author = Seeley, Boston Weather Forecast Office | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-10 | date = 1991-08-27 | title = Post-Storm Hurricane Report for Chatham, Massachusetts | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093649/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshchant.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshchant.gif | format = GIF}}</ref>。[[马萨葡萄园岛|马萨葡萄园岛]]的电器商店创下年度最佳销售业绩，一号电池脱销。许多居民购买电池和用电池供电的收音机及手电筒。美国总统[[乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什|乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什]]离开[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]的[[皮斯空军基地|皮斯空军基地]]，前往缅因州[[肯纳邦克波特_(缅因州)|肯纳邦克波特]]的家中暂避。为避免搭乘直升机可能产生的风险，他是乘坐汽车离开基地。为了方便总统通行，[[95号州际公路|95号州际公路]]部分路段封闭，但因有成千上万的居民正朝内陆转移，此举也导致多条公路拥堵，堵车距离达数英里长。<ref name="wp820" />新罕布什尔州共开设八间避难所<ref name="fema2" />，约有5200人从沿海地区撤离，其中大部分是游客<ref name="nh">{{cite report | author = Concord, New Hampshire National Weather Service | date = 1991-08-21 | title = Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshcon.gif | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510195017/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshcon.gif | dead-url = no }}</ref>。邻近的缅因州也开有49个避难所<ref name="fema2" />，[[约克县_(缅因州)|约克县]]沿海地区约有8600人疏散<ref name="wcm">{{cite web | author = Wayne Cotterly | date = 2002-10-21 | title = Hurricane Bob | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | url = http://www.pivot.net/~cotterly/bob.htm | archivedate = 2016-04-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160401071038/http://www.pivot.net/~cotterly/bob.htm }}</ref>。

面对飓风可能引发强烈涌浪的威胁，有关部门呼吁[[芬迪湾|芬迪湾]]的渔民返回港口躲避<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Kitchener – Waterloo Record | date = 1991-08-19 | title = Bob warnings : Hurricane lashes U.S. coast on way to Maritimes | page = A2}}</ref>。

