受飓风影响，[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]普降中雨并受到相当程度破坏，损失总额约有15亿美元（1991年美元），其中包括约7亿美元灾后清理成本、未投保财产损失和食品补助费用<ref name="TCR4">{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report Page Four | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim04.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233642/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim04.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF}}</ref>。这样高额的损失主要是因为风暴途经地区人口密集，鲍勃至此成为历史上令美国遭受损失第二大的热带气旋<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=O11BAAAAIBAJ&sjid=D6kMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3726,4832126&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Harlan Daily Enterprise | title = Hurricane Bob ranks no. 2 most expensive storm | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510195034/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=O11BAAAAIBAJ&sjid=D6kMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3726%2C4832126&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。而且截至2015年还能在所有吹袭美国本土的热带气旋中排到第32位<ref>{{cite journal | last3 = Landsea | first3 = Christopher W. | last1 = Blake | first1 = Eric S. | last2 = Gibney | first2 = Ethan J. | date = 2011-08-31| title = The deadliest, costliest, and most intense United States tropical cyclones from 1851 to 2010 (and other frequently requested hurricane facts) | publisher = National Oceanic Atmospheric Administration | journal = NOAA Technical Memorandum NWS-NHC-6 | page = 19 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/nws-nhc-6.pdf | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archivedate = 2016-08-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821210131/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/nws-nhc-6.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]]}}</ref><ref name="US hurricanes">{{cite web | title = Continental United States Hurricanes (Detailed Description) | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/UShurrs_detailed.html | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | author3 = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | date = 2015-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160828001543/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/UShurrs_detailed.html | deadurl = no | website = aoml.noaa.gov | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's Office of Oceanic & Atmospheric Research | location = Miami | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archivedate = 2016-08-28}}</ref><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160810161332/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | date = 2016-07-06 | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | archivedate = 2016-08-10}}</ref>。飓风沿途共导致210万人失去供电<ref>{{cite web | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report Page Five | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304131435/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim05.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim05.gif}}</ref>，另经确定还催生出六场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，可能还有13场未经确认的龙卷风<ref name="TCR3">{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report Page Three | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002020531/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim03.gif | format = GIF}}</ref>。

=== 南、北卡罗莱纳州和中大西洋地区 ===
风暴中心从南卡罗莱纳州以东数百英里洋面经过期间，该州受到的直接影响很小<ref name="TCR2" />。不过，气旋产生的大型涌浪在[[默特尔比奇_(南卡罗莱纳州)|默特尔比奇]]引发强烈[[回头浪|暗流]]，导致一名泳客溺毙<ref name="TDR1" /><ref name="TCR4" />。

一艘载有三人的小船从里特河（{{lang|en|Little River}}）出发前往罗得岛州，船的桅杆被飓风摧毁，三人被困在鲨鱼出没的开放海域随波逐流，经过12天的等待后才获[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]救援<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Bob Strands Three in Atlantic for 12 Days | date = 1991-09-01 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=c5A9AAAAIBAJ&sjid=0zUMAAAAIBAJ&pg=6722,68401&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510195144/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=c5A9AAAAIBAJ&sjid=0zUMAAAAIBAJ&pg=6722%2C68401&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

1991年8月18日，鲍勃掠过北卡罗莱纳州外滩群岛并产生狂风暴雨。虽然[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）的办公楼测得135毫米雨量，但外滩群岛内陆的降水很少。该州有一人因飓风丧生，损失总额估计为800万美元（1991年美元）。<ref name="TCR4" />[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]]小镇[[达克_(北卡罗莱纳州)|达克]]测得的持续风速为每小时100公里，比该州其他地区都高，阵风时速则以哈特拉斯角最高，有119公里<ref name="TCR9">{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report Page Nine | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194354/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim09.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim09.gif}}</ref>。[[钻石浅滩灯塔|钻石浅滩灯塔]]（{{lang|en|Diamond Shoal Light}}）在1991年8月18日深夜至19日凌晨测得每小时157.4公里的持续风速和197.6公里的阵风时速，并测得962.1毫巴（百帕）的最低气压<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ndbc.noaa.gov/data/climatic/DSLN7.txt | title = STATION: DSLN7 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | format = TXT | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195932/http://www.ndbc.noaa.gov/data/climatic/DSLN7.txt | archivedate = 2013-10-29}}</ref>。另外，哈特拉斯角还测得0.79至1.4米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref name="TCR9" />。

风暴产生暴雨和风暴潮，致使外滩群岛普遍发生洪灾。群岛通往外界的唯一公路[[北卡罗莱纳州12号州道|北卡罗莱纳州12号州道]]封闭，决定留下来等待风暴过去的人同外界的交通因此中断。狂风导致多条电缆中断，许多居民家中停电。<ref name="GBT1" />鲍勃外围[[雨带|雨带]]的[[飑线|飑线]]范围内共有六场龙卷风袭击北卡罗莱纳州，[[藤田级数|藤田级数]]为{{lang|en|F}}0至{{lang|en|F}}1级，但持续时间都很短<ref name="TCR4" />。其中[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]]出现的四场龙卷风共造成价值25万6000美元损失<ref name="NCDC">{{cite report | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | date = 1991-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160911113018/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-FAAFDC69-8238-43DF-B453-F46B23264D20.pdf | archivedate = 2016-09-11 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = NCDC Storm Events Database | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-FAAFDC69-8238-43DF-B453-F46B23264D20.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref>。哈特拉斯角附近有一幢房屋受到狂风的严重破坏，屋顶和部分壁板都不翼而飞<ref name="TDR1" />。

飓风在弗吉尼亚州东部经过期间降下小雨，阵风时速达到64公里。除弗吉尼亚海滩的[[桑布里奇_(弗吉尼亚州)|桑布里奇]]（{{lang|en|Sandbridge}}）受到轻度[[海蚀|海滩侵蚀]]外，没有报导表明当地受到重大破坏。<ref>{{cite web | author = Norfolk, VA National Weather Service | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1991-08-19 | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Bob | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212651/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshorf.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshorf.gif | deadurl = no}}</ref>

[[大洋城_(马里兰州)|大洋城]]因短时暴雨引发街道洪灾，沿海地区因大浪出现轻度海滩侵蚀和[[越流|越流]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Davis, Baltimore MD National Weather Service | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | deadurl = no | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Bob | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210539/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshbwi.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshbwi.gif | format = GIF | date = 1991-08-23}}</ref>。

特拉华州沿海地区出现强烈潮汐，最高达到1.8米<ref>{{cite report | author= Smelgus, Wilmington Delaware National Weather Service | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1991-08-20 | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Bob | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170032/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshilg.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshilg.gif}}</ref>。

更北面的[[泽西海岸|泽西海岸]]发生大面积海滩侵蚀，暴雨还引发街道洪灾<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Atlantic City National Weather Service | date = 1991-08-23 | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Bob... Corrected | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshacy.gif | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042107/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshacy.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。

除新英格兰以外，风暴在纽约州苏福克县[[布里奇汉普顿_(纽约州)|布里奇汉普顿]]（{{lang|en|Bridgehampton}}）产生的降水最多，有182毫米<ref>{{cite web | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in the Mid-Atlantic | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060511/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidatl.html | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidatl.html | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。长岛受到两场龙卷风袭击<ref name="TCR3" />，许多苹果、玉米和桃类作物被狂风摧毁<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Bangor Daily News | agency = Associated Press | title = Costs still climbing from Hurricane Bob | date = 1991-08-26 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=iq1JAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mg4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=1400,2818748&dq=hurricane+bob+new+york&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510195149/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=iq1JAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mg4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=1400%2C2818748&dq=hurricane+bob+new+york&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。当地刚刚经历干燥的夏季，突然爆发的洪灾致使大量土豆作物被毁，农作物损失数额达2000万美元<ref name="nyt" />，占农业产出总值的六分之一。[[长岛照明公司|长岛照明公司]]有约47万7765名用户失去供电，其中大部分生活在[[长岛东端|长岛东端]]，停电持续有近五天。受红绿灯失效影响，一人因交通事故丧生，<ref name="suf">{{cite report | publisher = Suffolk County, New York Government | date = 2008-10 | title = Section 5.4.4: Risk Assessment – Hurricane}}</ref>还有一名火车售票员被倒塌的树木砸死<ref name="fema1" />。大浪不但把近海的渔网摧毁<ref name="nyt">{{cite news | author = Sarah Bartlett | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | title = Between Heat and Hurricane, Summer Weather Is Weird | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306062008/http://www.nytimes.com/1991/09/02/nyregion/between-heat-and-hurricane-summer-weather-is-weird.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | date = 1991-09-02 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1991/09/02/nyregion/between-heat-and-hurricane-summer-weather-is-weird.html | publisher = The New York Times Company}}</ref>，还引发海滩侵蚀和海岸沿线大量船只被毁<ref name="suf" />。纽约州遭受的损失总额超过7500万美元<ref name="TCR3" />。

=== 新英格兰 ===
[[File:Hurricane_Bob_19_aug_1991_1818Z.jpg|right]]]]

鲍勃登陆新英格兰前直接从罗得岛州布洛克岛上空经过。岛上气象站在风暴北侧边缘附近测得时速169公里的阵风，表明气旋的实际风速有可能更强。<ref name="TCR3" />罗德岛州本土以[[华盛顿县_(罗得岛州)|华盛顿县]][[纳拉甘西特_(罗得岛州)|纳拉甘西特]]（{{lang|en|Narragansett}}）风速最高，达144公里。州首府[[普罗维登斯_(罗德岛州)|普罗维登斯]]的风暴潮有两米高，最高的[[萨康尼特河|萨康尼特河]]（{{lang|en|Sakonnet River}}）河口位置达五米。<ref name="TCR12">{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = Wind reports on Hurricane Bob in Connecticut and Rhode Island, August 1991 | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083816/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/prenhc/prelim12.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/prenhc/prelim12.gif}}</ref>萨康尼特河河口位置的风暴潮高度是按水位高涨后留下的痕迹估算，有可能受到波浪起伏的影响<ref name="TCR3" />。该州沿海地区因大浪引发严重海滩侵蚀，[[考文垂_(罗得岛州)|考文垂]]有多条道路被冲毁。[[波卡塞特河_(罗德岛州)|波卡塞特河]]（{{lang|en|Pocasset River}}）沿线发生洪灾。<ref name="ri" />全州以[[普罗维登斯县|普罗维登斯县]]的[[福斯特_(罗德岛州)|北福斯特]]（{{lang|en|North Foster}}）降雨量最高，达181毫米<ref name="New Eng">{{cite book | last1 = Roth | first1 = David M | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2012 | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall for the New England United States | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050333/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcnewengland.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcnewengland.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。风暴在该州行经地区共造成20万人失去供电<ref name="fema2" />，罗德岛州和马萨诸塞州东南部约有60%的居民家中停电<ref name="box">{{cite web | author1 = David R. Vallee | author2 = Michael R. Dion | publisher = Boston, MA National Weather Service | title = Hurricane Bob | date = 2005-12-05 | accessdate = 2015-11-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151130052551/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/box/hurricane/hurricaneBob.shtml | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/box/hurricane/hurricaneBob.shtml | archivedate = 2015-11-30}}</ref>。风暴期间，约有100万吨污水因溢流而流入纳拉甘西特湾<ref name="ap826">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 1991-08-26 | title = Costs Still Climbing from Hurricane Bob | newspaper = Bangor Daily news}}</ref>，罗得岛州的损失总额超过1亿1500万美元<ref name="TCR3" />。

从罗得岛州上空经过期间，鲍勃的狂风还向西延伸到康涅狄格州境内，该州以格罗顿附近风速最高，有每小时120公里，阵风时速更达160公里<ref name="TCR12" />。州内[[康涅狄格州行政区划|每个县]]都有树木被狂风刮倒，并以东南部沿海地区受大风破坏最为严重<ref name="hart">{{cite report | author = Hartford, Connecticut National Weather Service | date = 1991-08-23 | title = Preliminary Survey... Hurricane Bob | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshbdl1.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304113627/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshbdl1.gif | format = GIF}}</ref>。康涅狄格州约有31万5000人家中断电<ref name="fema1" />。[[温德姆县_(康涅狄格州)|温德姆县]][[斯特林_(康涅狄格州)|斯特林]]（{{lang|en|Sterling}}）有一名男子被掉落的树枝砸中后伤重不治<ref name="hart2">{{cite web | author = Hartford, Connecticut National Weather Service | date = 1991-08-23 | title = Preliminary Survey... Hurricane Bob (page 2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshbdl2.gif | format = GIF | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510195218/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshbdl2.gif | dead-url = no }}</ref>。全州以[[新伦敦_(康涅狄格州)|新伦敦]]的风暴潮最高，有1.5米<ref name="TCR12" />。沿海洪灾基本局限在[[新伦敦县_(康涅狄格州)|新伦敦县]]内，该县沿海地区受到的破坏程度很轻，但有一名女性因船只倾覆遇难<ref name="hart2" />。州内以[[诺威奇_(康涅狄格州)|诺威奇]]降雨总量最高，有158毫米<ref name="New Eng" />。洪灾程度很轻，基本局限在溪流和小河附近<ref name="hart" />。康涅狄格州遭受的损失总额估计在4900万美元，其中包括450万美元农作物损失。风暴经过期间有一人因火灾丧生，<ref name="hart" /><ref name="hwso">{{cite web | author = Bruce Budd, Hartford Weather Service Office | date = 1991-08-28 | title = Hurricane Bob Additional Information | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/bdl.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205210/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/bdl.gif}}</ref>另有五人遇难<ref name="TCR4" />。

马萨诸塞州是受飓风影响最严重的地区，损失总额超过十亿美元<ref name="end">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Reading Eagle | date = 1991-11-30 | title = Storm season is over | agency = Associated Press | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OM4xAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sOIFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2436,8339439&dq=hurricane+season&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archive-date = 2015-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150909053625/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OM4xAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sOIFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2436,8339439&dq=hurricane+season&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。位于[[巴泽兹湾|巴泽兹湾]]（{{lang|en|Buzzards Bay}}）的沿海自动气象观测站测得的最大持续风速为每小时124公里，阵风时速则达143公里<ref name="TCR3" />。该州以[[普罗威斯顿|普罗威斯顿]]的持续风速最高，达每小时161公里<ref name="TCR13">{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = Wind reports on Hurricane Bob in Rhode Island and Massachusetts, August 1991 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202843/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/prenhc/prelim13.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/prenhc/prelim13.gif | format = GIF | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>，[[巴恩斯特布尔县|巴恩斯特布尔县]]的[[布鲁斯特_(马萨诸塞州)|布鲁斯特]]（{{lang|en|Brewster}}）测得时速201公里的强烈阵风，但数据未获正式认可<ref>{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = Wind reports on Hurricane Bob in New England and Canada, August 1991 | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093639/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim15.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim15.gif}}</ref>。[[韦斯特菲尔德_(马萨诸塞州)|韦斯特菲尔德]]的降雨总量达179毫米，比州内其他地点都高<ref name="New Eng" />。该州以巴泽兹湾沿线的风暴潮最强，并以[[新贝德福德_(马萨诸塞州)|新贝德福德]]和巴恩斯特布尔县的[[伍兹霍尔|伍兹霍尔]]最高，有1.8米<ref name="TCR13" />。鳕鱼角的[[查塔姆灯塔|查塔姆灯塔]]（{{lang|en|Chatham Light}}）周边海滩被大浪侵蚀，留下1.5米高的峭壁<ref name="chant" />。包括马萨葡萄园岛和[[南塔克特|南塔克特]]南侧海岸在内的其他多个地点因侵蚀流失的沙子有15米深，当地许多船只受到重创<ref name="box" />。鳕鱼角的供电全部中断，全州有超过50万人家中停电<ref name="fema2" />。巴泽兹湾向东到鳕鱼角之间区域灾情最重，至少有61套房屋被毁，这些地区的苹果和桃树果园也受到沉重打击<ref name="box" />，农业损失总额估计在1000万美元左右，该州的公共财物还受到价值6900万美元的损失<ref name="ap826" />。

虽然鲍勃距新罕布什尔州最近时仍然位于海上，但该州还是出现大风，[[皮斯国民警卫队空军基地|皮斯国民警卫队空军基地]]的阵风时速达到97公里<ref>{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1992-08-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043243/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/prenhc/prelim14.gif | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | title = Hurricane Bob selected surface observations, August 1991 | format = GIF | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/prenhc/prelim14.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。[[华盛顿山_(新罕布什尔州)|华盛顿山]]在风暴期间共降下189毫米雨量<ref name="New Eng" />。[[洛弗尔河|洛弗尔河]]（{{lang|en|Lovell River}}）和[[康图库克河|康图库克河]]泛滥成灾，新罕布什尔州南部和中部城区发生大范围洪灾<ref name="nh" />。全州共有两人死亡，其中一人死于交通意外，另一人则是因船只倾覆遇难。狂风刮倒大量树木，还令许多输电线缆中断，<ref name="nh" />致使该州约三万人失去供电<ref name="fema2" />。州内损失总额估计在200万美元左右<ref name="TCR3" />。邻近的[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]以[[温德姆县_(佛蒙特州)|温德姆县]]的[[弗农_(佛蒙特州)|弗农]]（{{lang|en|Vernon}}）雨量最高，有108毫米<ref name="New Eng" />。

以热带风暴强度穿越缅因州期间，鲍勃产生的风力依然强劲，[[波特兰_(缅因州)|波特兰]]的阵风时速有110公里<ref name="port" />。[[威斯卡西特_(缅因州)|威斯卡西特]]一间气象站的仪器在测得每小时148公里的风速后失效，另一间气象站还测得时速150公里的强烈阵风<ref name="port2" />。该州共有16万9200用户在气旋来袭期间失去供电，其中部分一周后仍未恢复<ref name="port">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/portlnd1.gif | format = GIF | title = Hurricane Report: Bob | author = Joseph A. Ronco | date = 1991-09-18 | work = Portland National Weather Service | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030932/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/portlnd1.gif}}</ref>。[[萨默塞特县_(缅因州)|萨默塞特县]]的[[圣奥尔本斯_(缅因州)|圣奥尔本斯]]（{{lang|en|St. Albans}}）出现一场龙卷风，令部分房屋受损，还把一间船屋刮离原地三个街区远<ref name="port2">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121026031243/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/portlnd2.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/portlnd2.gif | format = GIF | title = Hurricane Report: Bob (page 2) | author = Joseph A. Ronco | date = 1991-09-18 | work = Portland National Weather Service | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archivedate = 2012-01-26}}</ref>，不过这场龙卷风的存在未经正式确认<ref name="TCR3" />。气旋经过期间产生0.84米的风暴潮<ref name="port" />，[[波特兰国际喷气机机场|波特兰国际喷气机机场]]降下209毫米雨量，是鲍勃在全美产生降水最多的所在<ref name="brain">{{cite report | last = Roth | first = David M | date = 2007-04-30 | title = Hurricane Bob — August 18–21, 1991 | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065051/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/bob1991.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/bob1991.html}}</ref>，1991年8月也至此成为波特兰历史上最潮湿的月份<ref>{{cite report |author=Gray, Maine National Weather Service |date=2011-09-09 |title=The Portland ME Climate Summary for the Month of August 2011 |accessdate=2011-09-18 |url=http://www.maine.gov/mema/weather/pwmclmpwm |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61nIvVgIO?url=http://www.maine.gov/mema/weather/pwmclmpwm |archivedate=2011-09-18 }}</ref>。199毫米的24小时降雨量同样创下新纪录，但在1996年10月被降水经[[1996年飓风丽丽|飓风丽丽]]加强的温带天气系统打破。风暴产生的降雨还令[[普雷桑普斯科特河|普雷桑普斯科特河]]沿线流量创下新纪录，但该纪录同样被1996年的温带系统超越<ref>{{cite report | author = John W. Cannon | date = 2000-09 | title = A Hydrometeorological Assessment of the October 1996 Record Rainstorm in Maine | publisher = Eastern Region Headquarters | accessdate = 2012-10-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020153214/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/gyx/pdf/ta2000-02.pdf | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/gyx/pdf/ta2000-02.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref>。缅因州西南部有多座桥梁和多条道路被泛滥的河流冲毁，一名男子被洪水卷走后遇难，海上另有一人在救生筏中死亡<ref name="wcm" />。共有700套房屋受到风暴影响，其中一套被毁，另有三套受到严重破坏<ref name="maap">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 1991-09-16 | title = No aid for storm damage to Maine private property | newspaper = Bangor Daily News | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=brFJAAAAIBAJ&sjid=yg4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=4743,227463&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510195319/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=brFJAAAAIBAJ&sjid=yg4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=4743%2C227463&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。波特兰周边地区的损失总额超过2570万美元，还有三人丧生<ref name="port" />。

=== 加拿大大西洋省份 ===
袭击美国多州并造成重大破坏后，鲍勃的残留进入加拿大大西洋省份<ref name="TCR4" />。该国以新不伦瑞克北部降水最多，达111毫米。[[圣约翰斯_(纽芬兰-拉布拉多)|圣约翰斯]]在风暴期间测得创纪录的26毫米雨量。气旋在多地产生阵风，新斯科舍[[迪格比_(新斯科舍)|迪格比]]（{{lang|en|Digby}}）的风速达到每小时109公里。<ref name="chc">{{cite web | author = Canadian Hurricane Centre | date = 2010-09-14 | title = 1991-Bob | accessdate = 2016-09-11 | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=FD4D2BBE-1 | archivedate = 2016-08-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160816220159/http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=FD4D2BBE-1 | deadurl = no}}</ref>新斯科舍有两名17岁少女在福处角（{{lang|en|Cape Forchu}}）附近被强烈的涌浪卷走<ref name="TS2">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Toronto Star | date = 1991-08-20 | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | title = Storm sweeps 2 teens to sea 'The wave just sucked them away . . . The ocean was wild' | page = A3 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/doc/436456160.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=Staff-CP-AP&pub=Toronto%20Star&edition=&startpage=&desc=Storm%20sweeps%202%20teens%20to%20sea%20%27The%20wave%20just%20sucked%20them%20away%20.%20.%20.%20The%20ocean%20was%20wild%27 | archive-date = 2017-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171025155252/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/doc/436456160.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=Staff-CP-AP&pub=Toronto%20Star&edition=&startpage=&desc=Storm%20sweeps%202%20teens%20to%20sea%20%27The%20wave%20just%20sucked%20them%20away%20.%20.%20.%20The%20ocean%20was%20wild%27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，虽有救援人员立即出动营救<ref name="TS1">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Toronto Star | date = 1991-08-20 | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | title = Hurricane Bob lashes coast 2 swept out to sea as storm hits Nova Scotia | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/doc/436457999.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=CP-AP&pub=Toronto%20Star&edition=&startpage=&desc=Hurrican%20Bob%20lashes%20coast%202%20swept%20out%20to%20sea%20as%20storm%20hits%20Nova%20Scotia | page = A3 | archive-date = 2016-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160827192400/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/doc/436457999.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=CP-AP&pub=Toronto%20Star&edition=&startpage=&desc=Hurrican%20Bob%20lashes%20coast%202%20swept%20out%20to%20sea%20as%20storm%20hits%20Nova%20Scotia | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但之后经确认两人依然溺毙<ref name="TCR4" />。新不伦瑞克的[[弗雷德里克顿|弗雷德里克顿]]风速达到热带风暴标准，引起部分树木倒塌和电缆中断，局部地区因此停电。风暴还产生[[闪电|闪电]]，击中当地部分树木。<ref name="TS1" />[[潘特－韦尔特_(新不伦瑞克)|潘特－韦尔特]]（{{lang|en|Pointe-Verte}}）一幢两层高的民居在狂风下倒塌。[[佩蒂特－罗彻_(新不伦瑞克)|佩蒂特－罗彻]]（{{lang|en|Petit-Rocher}}）的港口有五艘渔船被涌浪淹没后沉没。当地消防员8月20日夜间在全城通宵排查，检查是否有中断的电缆或倒塌的树木。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | page = A12 | work = Kitchener – Waterloo Record | date = 1991-08-21 | title = Hurricane blows out after leaving trail of destruction}}</ref>爱德华王子岛也出现停电，芬迪湾的[[大马南岛|大马南岛]]一共受到价值约100万[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]（1991年加拿大元）的破坏<ref name="chc" />。

== 善后 ==
飓风过去后，长岛照明公司派出165名工作人员恢复长岛各地供电。康涅狄格州政府官员调遣约200辆卡车清理道路上的各种垃圾。马萨诸塞州国民警卫队出动协助救灾工作。<ref name="fema1" />罗得岛州有一名男子在尝试修复鲍勃造成的破坏时丧生<ref>{{cite news | author = David Crombie | title = Worker electrocuted in Westport 3 others hurt while moving house damaged in hurricane | newspaper = Journal-Bulletin Staff Writer | date = 1991-09-17 | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | url = http://www.pqarchiver.com/titles?dids=579135001:579135001&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Sep+17%252C+1991&author=DAVE+CROMBIE+Journal-Bulletin+Staff+Writer&pub=The+Providence+Journal&desc=Worker+electrocuted+in+Westport+3+others+hurt+while+moving+house+damaged+in+hurricane&pqatl=google | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306184200/http://www.pqarchiver.com/titles?dids=579135001:579135001&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Sep+17,+1991&author=DAVE+CROMBIE+Journal-Bulletin+Staff+Writer&pub=The+Providence+Journal&desc=Worker+electrocuted+in+Westport+3+others+hurt+while+moving+house+damaged+in+hurricane&pqatl=google | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>，该州海滩在风暴过去五天后恢复开放<ref name="rj">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 1991-08-25 | title = Massachusetts fights to recover from Hurricane Bob | newspaper = Record-Journal | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=4EJIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ZAENAAAAIBAJ&pg=1402,3853215&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510195409/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=4EJIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ZAENAAAAIBAJ&pg=1402%2C3853215&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。飓风将[[长岛海湾|长岛海湾]]的水强力混合起来，使当地未像往年夏季一样出现蓝藻爆发<ref>{{cite news | author = Elsa Brenner | date = 1991-10-06 | newspaper = The New York Times | title = Shore Communities Assess Implications Of L.I. Sound Study | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | publisher = The New York Times Company | archivedate = 2016-05-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160531143656/http://www.nytimes.com/1991/10/06/nyregion/shore-communities-assess-implications-of-li-sound-study.html?src=pm | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1991/10/06/nyregion/shore-communities-assess-implications-of-li-sound-study.html?src=pm}}</ref>。风暴过后的几天里，[[NSTAR_(公司)|马萨诸塞州电气公司]]安排工作人员每天工作16小时在全州各地恢复电力，还从外界聘请人员协助<ref name="ap826" />。除鳕鱼角地区外，马萨诸塞州大部分居民的供电都在五天内恢复<ref name="rj" />。飓风在夏季接近尾声时来袭，对本已陷入[[20世纪90年代初经济衰退|衰退]]的旅游业雪上加霜<ref name="ap826" />。飓风过去约两个月后，新英格兰沿海地区又受到人称[[1991年完美风暴|完美风暴]]的强烈东北风暴袭击，部分地点遭受的破坏程度比鲍勃来袭时还要严重<ref name="maine">{{cite news | author = William C. Hidlay | date = 1991-11-01 | title = Maine hit hard by storm | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Bangor Daily News | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DqhJAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KQ4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=3345,8099&dq=storm+new+england&hl=en | archive-date = 2015-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150909075230/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DqhJAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KQ4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=3345,8099&dq=storm+new+england&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

面对气旋造成的重大破坏，美国总统乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什宣布罗得岛州、马萨诸塞州、缅因州、康涅狄格州、新罕布什尔州和纽约州为灾区<ref>{{cite web | publisher = [[联邦紧急事务管理局|Federal Emergency Management Agency]] | date = 2005-05-23 | title = 1991 Federal Disaster Declarations | accessdate = 2012-06-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120618055926/http://www.fema.gov/news/disasters.fema?year=1991 | archivedate = 2012-06-18 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/disasters.fema?year=1991}}</ref>。不过，缅因州受到的破坏程度还没有严重到各个家庭可以分别申请援助的程度<ref name="maap" />。成为灾区的城市可以动用联邦资金支付大部分垃圾清理、公共建筑维修费用及其他市政开支。但是，[[美国联邦政府|联邦政府]]并没有在总统宣布过后立即向灾区提供援助，这一定程度上是因为布什总统认为鲍勃属于“灾难，但不属于紧急情况”，导致救灾拨款被其他预算需求占用，未能及时送抵灾区。总统此举主要是为了同[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]主控的[[第101届联邦国会|国会]]对抗，国会当时要求政府加急处理救灾事务。<ref>{{cite news | author = John Diamond | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Hour | date = 1991-10-18 | title = Congress Attempting to Speed Up Disaster Funds | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=dwYhAAAAIBAJ&sjid=f3YFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3033,2422725&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510195401/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=dwYhAAAAIBAJ&sjid=f3YFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3033%2C2422725&dq=hurricane+bob&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>

面对这场飓风造成的重大破坏，[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]于1992年春将风暴名称“鲍勃”退役，今后永远都不会再在[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风]]命名时采用<ref>{{cite web | date = 2011-03-16 | accessdate = 2016-09-12 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml#retired | title = Retired Hurricane Names Since 1954 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160905012300/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml#retired | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-09-05}}</ref>。用于取代的新名称是“比尔”（{{lang|en|Bill}}），于[[1997年大西洋飓风季|1997年]]首度启用<ref name="HURDAT" />。

